{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-340-crazy-function","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 340: Luda funkcija","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Za konstante cele brojeve $a$, $b$, $c$, definisaćemo funkciju $F(n)$ na sledeći način:</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{align}\n&#x26; F(n) = n - c \\;\\text{ kwa wote } n > b \\\\\n&#x26; F(n) = F(a + F(a + F(a + F(a + n)))) \\;\\text{ kwa wote } n ≤ b.\n\\end{align}$$</p>\n<p>Pia, definiši $S(a, b, c) = \\displaystyle\\sum_{n = 0}^b F(n)$.</p>\n<p>Primer, ako su $a = 50$, $b = 2000$ i $c = 40$, onda je $F(0) = 3240$ i $F(2000) = 2040$. Takođe, $S(50, 2000, 40) = 5\\,204\\,240$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi poslednje 9 cifara za $S({21}^7, 7^{21}, {12}^7)$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4c21000cf542c50ffd4","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301999,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-340-crazy-function"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function crazyFunction() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\ncrazyFunction();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>crazyFunction()</code> bi trebalo da vrati <code>291504964</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(crazyFunction(), 291504964);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-301-to-400","dashedName":"problem-340-crazy-function","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chap